<H1><FONT SIZE="+3" FACE="lucida sans">PRIVATE PRESSES OF THE UK</FONT></H1>
<HR></TD>
<TD><IMG SRC="balls/ppukblob.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM" WIDTH="119" HEIGHT="48"></TD></TR></TABLE>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>
<P align="justify">Perhaps one of the best kept secrets of art and craft in the UK is its
private presses - there is much splendid work to be had from the home of
Kelmscott, Doves, and Ashendene. This web page presents a number of presses who
are actively producing books in the UK by letterpress and generally with
original illustrations to accompany new texts. Orders should be placed directly
with the presses.</P>
    <p>&nbsp;</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="center">
